{"tid":1618229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不被仇恨支配] 飼養鶳的正確方法","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:01:21.000Z","uid":118767,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1228e9431944d300ef92cd956ef74909b1bff62c","tid":1618229,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"近期香城掀起飼養鶳熱潮，但部份新手馴獸師缺乏飼養經驗，導致零星鶳餵食意外發生，包括鶳錯手傷及手足家屬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦有殘障人士被鶳誤會而受到攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，較具爭議嘅有armless廢老因撕走文宣而觸動鶳神經，以上例子雖屬不幸，受襲者亦並非全然無辜，但難免影響鶳形象，更造成鶳愛好者之間嘅批鬥耗損。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，喺互助互信嘅基礎下，作為一班願意檢討同改善嘅文明鶳愛好者，在此分享一套「正義戰爭理論 (Just War Theory)」飼養原則供大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我哋明白世上從來都冇永恆不變、絕對啱或錯嘅飼養、召喚原則，但我哋可以根據氣候、環境、天敵形態等外在因素制定最適合時宜嘅方針，只要形勢不變，希望大家願意跟從，唔好令普羅大眾對咁可愛嘅神獸烙下壞印象。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">區別原則（Discrimination）</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n只能鶳主動攻擊市民嘅藍屍。<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">使用武力具有必要性（Necessity）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果唔鶳，將有更多的平民受襲，喺無可選擇嘅情況下，鶳係作為阻止更大暴力嘅最後手段。<br />\n<br />\n3.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相稱性／比例原則（proportionality）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n只還以相應受襲程度的鶳，廢老投降就要停手。<br />\n<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公共說服：抗爭者應當對任何武力行為向公眾交代，進行公共說</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個講到口都爛，市民未必睇到晒前因後果，所以一定要解釋鶳原因！<br />\n<br />\n有錯請補充及糾正，要屌請細紬力啲屌，會痛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家勿忘飼養初衷，齊齊做個負責任嘅主人，唔好俾神獸引導、支配情緒，懇請大家謹記，與怪物戰鬥時，要小心自己不要也變成怪物。祝大家武運昌盛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n附上我家鶳近照一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ibb.co/Kmhr7f9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fibb.co%2FKmhr7f9&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=aee36239\" target=\"_blank\">https://ibb.co/Kmhr7f9</a><br />\n<br />\n參考來源：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B4%94%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E4%BB%A5%E6%%A6%E5%88%B6%E6%9A%B4%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87-%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87-%E6%95%88%E7%94%A8%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87-%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B4%2594%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A1%2593%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25%25A6%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2589%2587-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587-%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=e59fdbf6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25B4%2594%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A1%2593%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25%25A6%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%2589%2587-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587-%25E6%2595%2588%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258E%259F%25E5%2589%2587-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%2F&h=72d5e4e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%B4%94%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96-%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E4%BB%A5%E6%%A6%E5%88%B6%E6%9A%B4%E5%AE%88%E5%89%87-%E6%AD%A3%E7%BE%A9%E5%8E%9F%E5%89%87-%E6%95%88%E7%94%A8%E5%8E%9F%E5%